refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;

 voidPhar::addEmptyDir
 stringdirname

&phar.write;



 With this method, an empty directory is created with path dirname.
 This method is similar to ZipArchive::addEmptyDir.

&reftitle.parameters;




   dirname



     The name of the empty directory to create in the phar archive

  &reftitle.examples;



    A Phar::addEmptyDir example


<?php
try {
    $a = new Phar('/path/to/phar.phar');

    $a->addEmptyDir('/full/path/to/file');
    // demonstrates how this file is stored
    $b = $a['full/path/to/file']->isDir();
} catch (Exception $e) {
    // handle errors here
}
?>
